{"id":861,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":861,"title":"Ezekiel 33","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 33"],[".studySummary",["i","Watchmen who raise the warning voice save their own souls—Repentant sinners are saved—The righteous who turn to sin are damned—The people of Judah in Jerusalem are destroyed because of their sins."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.1","order":"02.27.033.57343"},["b","1"],"Again the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.2","order":"02.27.033.57344"},["b","2"],"Son of man, speak to the children of thy people, and say unto them, When I bring the sword upon a land, if the people of the land take a man of their coasts, and set him for their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"watchman"],":"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.3","order":"02.27.033.57345"},["b","3"],"If when he seeth the sword come upon the land, he blow the trumpet, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"warn"],"the people;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.4","order":"02.27.033.57346"},["b","4"],"Then whosoever heareth the sound of the trumpet, and taketh not warning; if the sword come, and take him away, his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"blood"],"shall be upon his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"own"],"head."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.5","order":"02.27.033.57347"},["b","5"],"He heard the sound of the trumpet, and took not warning; his blood shall be upon him. But he that taketh warning shall deliver his soul."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.6","order":"02.27.033.57348"},["b","6"],"But if the watchman see the sword come, and blow not the trumpet, and the people be not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"warned"],"; if the sword come, and take",["i","any"],"person from among them, he is taken away in his iniquity; but his blood will I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"require"],"at the watchman’s hand."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.7","order":"02.27.033.57349"},["b","7"],"¶So thou, O son of man, I have set thee a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"watchman"],"unto the house of Israel; therefore thou shalt hear the word at my mouth, and warn them from me."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.8","order":"02.27.033.57350"},["b","8"],"When I say unto the wicked, O wicked",["i","man,"],"thou shalt surely die; if thou dost not speak to warn the wicked from his way, that wicked",["i","man"],"shall die in his iniquity; but his blood will I require at thine hand."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.9","order":"02.27.033.57351"},["b","9"],"Nevertheless, if thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"warn"],"the wicked of his way to turn from it; if he do not turn from his way, he shall die in his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"iniquity"],"; but thou hast delivered thy soul."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.10","order":"02.27.033.57352"},["b","10"],"Therefore, O thou son of man, speak unto the house of Israel; Thus ye speak, saying, If our transgressions and our sins",["i","be"],"upon us, and we pine away in them, how should we then live?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.11","order":"02.27.033.57353"},["b","11"],"Say unto them,",["i","As"],"I live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", I have no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"pleasure"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"death"],"of the wicked; but that the wicked turn from his way and live: turn ye, turn ye from your evil ways; for why will ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"die"],", O house of Israel?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.12","order":"02.27.033.57354"},["b","12"],"Therefore, thou son of man, say unto the children of thy people, The righteousness of the righteous shall not deliver him in the day of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"transgression"],": as for the wickedness of the wicked, he shall not fall thereby in the day that he turneth from his wickedness; neither shall the righteous be able to live for his",["i","righteousness"],"in the day that he sinneth."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.13","order":"02.27.033.57355"},["b","13"],"When I shall say to the righteous,",["i","that"],"he shall surely live; if he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"trust"],"to his own righteousness, and commit",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"iniquity"],", all his righteousnesses shall not be remembered; but for his iniquity that he hath committed, he shall die for it."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.14","order":"02.27.033.57356"},["b","14"],"Again, when I say unto the wicked, Thou shalt surely",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"die"],"; if he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"turn"],"from his sin, and do that which is lawful and right;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.15","order":"02.27.033.57357"},["b","15"],["i","If"],"the wicked",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"restore"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"pledge"],", give again that he had robbed, walk in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"statutes"],"of life, without committing iniquity; he shall surely live, he shall not die."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.16","order":"02.27.033.57358"},["b","16"],"None of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"sins"],"that he hath committed shall be mentioned unto him: he hath done that which is lawful and right; he shall surely live."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.17","order":"02.27.033.57359"},["b","17"],"¶Yet the children of thy people say, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"way"],"of the Lord is not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"equal"],": but as for them, their way is not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"equal"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.18","order":"02.27.033.57360"},["b","18"],"When the righteous",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"turneth"],"from his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"righteousness"],", and committeth iniquity, he shall even die thereby."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.19","order":"02.27.033.57361"},["b","19"],"But if the wicked turn from his wickedness, and do that which is lawful and right, he shall live thereby."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.20","order":"02.27.033.57362"},["b","20"],"¶Yet ye say, The way of the Lord is not equal. O ye house of Israel, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"judge"],"you every one after his ways."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21","order":"02.27.033.57363"},["b","21"],"¶And it came to pass in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"twelfth"],"year of our captivity, in the tenth",["i","month,"],"in the fifth",["i","day"],"of the month,",["i","that"],"one that had",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"escaped"],"out of Jerusalem came unto me, saying, The",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"city"],"is smitten."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.22","order":"02.27.033.57364"},["b","22"],"Now the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"hand"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was upon me in the evening, afore he that was escaped came; and had opened my mouth, until he came to me in the morning; and my mouth was opened, and I was no more",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"dumb"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.23","order":"02.27.033.57365"},["b","23"],"Then the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.24","order":"02.27.033.57366"},["b","24"],"Son of man, they that inhabit those",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"wastes"],"of the land of Israel speak, saying, Abraham was one, and he inherited the land: but we",["i","are"],"many; the land is given us for inheritance."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.25","order":"02.27.033.57367"},["b","25"],"Wherefore say unto them, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Ye eat with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"blood"],", and lift up your eyes toward your idols, and shed blood: and shall ye possess the land?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.26","order":"02.27.033.57368"},["b","26"],"Ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"stand upon your sword"],", ye work abomination, and ye defile every one his neighbour’s wife: and shall ye possess the land?"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.27","order":"02.27.033.57369"},["b","27"],"Say thou thus unto them, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],";",["i","As"],"I live, surely they that",["i","are"],"in the wastes shall fall by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"sword"],", and him that",["i","is"],"in the open field will I give to the beasts to be devoured, and they that",["i","be"],"in the forts and in the caves shall die of the pestilence."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.28","order":"02.27.033.57370"},["b","28"],"For I will lay the land most desolate, and the pomp of her strength shall cease; and the mountains of Israel shall be desolate, that none shall pass through."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.29","order":"02.27.033.57371"},["b","29"],"Then shall they know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", when I have laid the land most desolate because of all their abominations which they have committed."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.30","order":"02.27.033.57372"},["b","30"],"¶Also, thou son of man, the children of thy people still are talking against thee by the walls and in the doors of the houses, and speak one to another, every one to his brother, saying, Come, I pray you, and hear what is the word that cometh forth from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.31","order":"02.27.033.57373"},["b","31"],"And they come unto thee as the people cometh, and they sit before thee",["i","as"],"my people, and they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"hear"],"thy words, but they will not do them: for with their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"mouth"],"they shew much love,",["i","but"],"their heart goeth after their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"covetousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.32","order":"02.27.033.57374"},["b","32"],"And, lo, thou",["i","art"],"unto them as a very lovely song of one that hath a pleasant voice, and can play well on an instrument: for they hear thy words, but they do them not."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.33","order":"02.27.033.57375"},["b","33"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"when"],"this cometh to pass, (lo, it will come,) then shall they know that a prophet hath been among them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.2a","order":"02.27.033.57376"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.18"},"3 Ne. 16:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.45.45,53-54"},"D&C 101:45 (45, 53–54)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.3a","order":"02.27.033.57378"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"TG Warn"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.4a","order":"02.27.033.57380"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.13"},"Ezek. 18:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.6"},"Acts 18:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.4b","order":"02.27.033.57382"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.6a","order":"02.27.033.57384"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.81.81-82"},"D&C 88:81 (81–82)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.6b","order":"02.27.033.57386"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.7a","order":"02.27.033.57388"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"TG Leadership"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watchman"},"Watchman"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.9a","order":"02.27.033.57390"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-magnifying-callings-within"},"TG Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.9b","order":"02.27.033.57392"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.21"},"1 Ne. 10:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.11a","order":"02.27.033.57394"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.23"},"Ezek. 18:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.30"},"Mosiah 26:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/29.20"},"29:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.39"},"Moses 7:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.11b","order":"02.27.033.57396"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-mercy-of"},"TG God, Mercy of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.11c","order":"02.27.033.57398"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.31"},"Ezek. 18:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.12a","order":"02.27.033.57400"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20"},"Ezek. 3:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24"},"18:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.13a","order":"02.27.033.57402"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/trustworthiness"},"TG Trustworthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.13b","order":"02.27.033.57404"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.14a","order":"02.27.033.57406"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18"},"Ezek. 3:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.14b","order":"02.27.033.57408"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.27"},"Ezek. 18:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.15a","order":"02.27.033.57410"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"TG Reconciliation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.15b","order":"02.27.033.57412"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.7"},"Ezek. 18:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.15c","order":"02.27.033.57414"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.5"},"Lev. 18:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.16a","order":"02.27.033.57416"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.17a","order":"02.27.033.57418"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.25.25,27"},"Ezek. 18:25 (25, 27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.17b","order":"02.27.033.57420"},["b","17b"],["span.small","HEB"],"right or just."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.17c","order":"02.27.033.57422"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.18a","order":"02.27.033.57424"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.18b","order":"02.27.033.57426"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.20a","order":"02.27.033.57428"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.30"},"Ezek. 18:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.20"},"1 Ne. 10:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21a","order":"02.27.033.57430"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.2"},"Ezek. 1:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.1"},"20:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.1"},"24:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/26.1"},"26:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21b","order":"02.27.033.57432"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.26"},"Ezek. 24:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21c","order":"02.27.033.57434"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jerusalem"},"TG Jerusalem"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.22a","order":"02.27.033.57436"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.3"},"Ezek. 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.22b","order":"02.27.033.57438"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.27"},"Ezek. 24:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.24a","order":"02.27.033.57440"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.4"},"Ezek. 36:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.25a","order":"02.27.033.57442"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-eating-of"},"TG Blood, Eating of"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.26a","order":"02.27.033.57444"},["b","26a"],["span.small","IE"],"resort to violence."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.27a","order":"02.27.033.57446"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.17"},"Ezek. 5:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.21"},"14:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.8"},"Rev. 6:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.31a","order":"02.27.033.57448"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.15"},"Matt. 11:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/5.11.11-14"},"Heb. 5:11 (11–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.31"},"2 Ne. 9:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.14"},"D&C 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.31b","order":"02.27.033.57450"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13"},"Isa. 29:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.8.7-8"},"Matt. 15:8 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.46"},"Luke 6:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.28"},"Alma 34:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.19"},"JS—H 1:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"31c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.31c","order":"02.27.033.57452"},["b","31c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.36"},"Ps. 119:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/57.17"},"Isa. 57:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.33a","order":"02.27.033.57454"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/2.5"},"Ezek. 2:5"],"."]]}
